            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Vulcaci&amp;lt;o=Q&amp;gt; Rufino et <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avio</ex></expan> Eusebio <expan><abbr>conss</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan> Kalendis <lb n="2"/>Augustis <lb n="3"/>cum cibes <note>sic</note> frequentes coloniae Paestanorum in uno <lb n="4"/>adfuissent consilioque habito berba <note>sic</note> fecerunt cum <lb n="5"/>tot tantaque beneficia sblendentia <note>sic</note> de domo Aquilini Nes<lb break="no" n="6"/>tori probi adulescentis descendant quibus colonia nos<lb break="no" n="7"/>tra exornata unicuique nobis cibibus <note>sic</note> in oculis adque <note>sic</note> <lb n="8"/>animis sint praecipuae cum unusquisque civium se con<lb break="no" n="9"/>berterit <note>sic</note> opera ab his extructa oculis eorum occurrant <lb n="10"/>sic faciem cibitatis <note>sic</note> honestam reddant utinam qui tantus <lb n="11"/>populus esset status ut tantis muneribus domus eorum <lb n="12"/>aliis quoque gloriosis muneribus remunerandus esset <lb n="13"/>fateri beneficia eius munera populi intebimque <note>sic</note> contentos <lb n="14"/>esse hoc munere flaminis gratulit quod publica voce <lb n="15"/>et offerendum etiam cibes <note>sic</note> cupi<expan><ex>v</ex><abbr>erant</abbr></expan> cum Aquilius Nesto<lb break="no" n="16"/>rius contemplatione mutui honoris nos municipes sua <lb n="17"/>dignatione unice diligat sitque similem nobis adfec<lb break="no" n="18"/>tionem etiam Aquilius Aper filius <expan><abbr>efu</abbr><ex>s</ex></expan> <note>sic</note> praebiturus <lb n="19"/>placere cibibus <note>sic</note> patronatus cibitatis <note>sic</note> eidem offerri <lb n="20"/>ut fulti patrocinio eorum populus noster plus ho<lb break="no" n="21"/>noris consecutus quam optulisset <note>sic</note> videatur <lb n="22"/>quod fieri placere de ea re ita censuerunt <lb n="23"/>feliciter 
            </ab></div>
